<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'pages', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
<section class="jumbotron text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <%= image_tag "lospolloshermanos.png"%><br>
    <h1 class="topic">LOS POLLOS HERMANOS</h1><br>
    <h4 class="text-center">TASTE THE FAMILY</h4><br><hr>
    <p class="lead text-muted">Los Pollos Hermanos knows what family tastes like and we bring that warmth and goodness into our food every single day. We always have something delicious cooking, be it our crispy fried chicken, new spicy curly fries, or delicious dipping sauces.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/orders/new" class="btn btn-danger 4"><%=fa_icon "cart-arrow-down"%>
        Order Now</a>
      <a href="/books/new" class="btn btn-warning my-4"><%=fa_icon "bookmark"%>
        Book Table</a>
    </p>
    <h6 class="telephone text-center">
      <%=fa_icon "phone"%>
      567-768477</h6><br>

    <h5 class="address text-center">
      <%=fa_icon "map-marker"%>
      Lakeside, Pokhara</h5>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="card-deck">
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag "rest.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top w-100", :height=>"300" %>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title text-center">Healthy food and healthy Environment</h5>
      <p class="card-text text-center">We cook food from the organic and fresh products. For eating we have diffferent sections for parties and celebrations. So the chance of disturbance is almost zero.</p>
      <p class="card-text"></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag "rest2.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top w-100", :height=>"300" %>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title text-center">Experienced Cooks</h5>
      <p class="card-text text-center">Our cooks are among the best cooks of Nepal right now. They all well experienced and make the best food.</p>
      <p class="card-text"></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag "rest3.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top w-100", :height=>"300"%>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title text-center">Report</h5>
      <p class="card-text text-center">If you find any problem in our services, please report the problem and we will try to solve as soon as possible
      </p>
      <p class="card-text">
        <center>
          <a href="/reports/new" class="btn btn-outline-danger ">Report</a>
        </center>

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><br>

<section>
  <h1 class=" tasty text-center my-4">Our Tasty Menu</h1>
  <center>
    <%= render 'pages/menu' %>
  </center>
